# Build-context excludes for every image built from the repo root.
#
# packages/qaroom-mcp depends on @qaroom/content + @qaroom/gateway (workspace:*), but each service
# image copies `packages/` wholesale while copying only its OWN service — so including qaroom-mcp makes
# `pnpm install` fail with ERR_PNPM_WORKSPACE_PKG_NOT_FOUND (the cross-service deps aren't in the image).
# No service imports qaroom-mcp (it's the standalone cross-service MCP server), so it is never needed
# inside a service/web image. Excluding it lets the per-service installs resolve.
packages/qaroom-mcp

# Never ship local installs, VCS, or build output into any image context.
**/node_modules
.git
**/dist
**/.venv
**/.turbo
